Game 2 - Agent-Goal Behavior

player must eat all prey - eating one prey spouts 2 more predators
player must avoid predators and obstacles and get to the the finish point
player must collect a certain number of objects falling from the surface or lying on the ground


minmax strategist - fish game board

Convert a series of nested nodes into a doubly linked list or list
Use binary trees and different node traversal (inorder, preorder, and postorder) to get different paths along the tree

create gambling scenario - bet on fish - based on rules - orange fish hunt pink fish but avoid blue fish, blue fish hunt pink fish orange fish but avoid pink fish, etc...  GKGoals are added dynamically based on which fish are present

    -weights for avoid predator/chasing prey
    -speed at which prey are chased

